<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈拿着一把斧子跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，杰克？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬起头，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>云层下面竟然有一双腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是食人魔的腿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克抓起斧子用力砍了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔大喊：“我来啦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克砍得更用力了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！杰克砍断了豆茎！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨大的豆茎开始往下倒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”食人魔从豆茎上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！他重重地掉在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，豆茎也倒了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔被压在豆茎的下面，一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金竖琴突然响起了音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是我的新主人！”金竖琴唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈抱住了杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没事，太好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要再有什么魔豆和计划了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了：“还有最后一个计划！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈又开始担心了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了笑：“别担心！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你会喜欢这个计划的，我保证！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都很喜欢金竖琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克用它赚了很多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给穷人们食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给妈妈盖了大大的新房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克还盖了其他东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，杰克敲了敲伊丽莎的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请跟我来！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把伊莉莎带到了他的家旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里还有一座新盖的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是给你和家人的。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那晚的夜空中，有一颗星星闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从此，大家都过上了幸福的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>